[/vc_column_text][/trx_content][/trx_section][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][trx_content][trx_title type="2" align="center" animation="fadeInRight" css="margin-top: 1.44em;" bottom="medium"]News &amp; Events[/trx_title][trx_blogger style="masonry_3" descr="130" cat="21" count="3" offset="0" animation="fadeIn"][/trx_content][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content_no_spaces"][vc_column][trx_section bg_image="954" bg_tile="" css="background-position:center;padding: 2.4em 0px;"][trx_content][trx_block class="max_width_responsive" css="max-width: 640px;"][trx_title type="3" animation="fadeInLeft" css="margin-bottom: .5em;"]Youth Fire Stop Prevention &amp; Intervention Program[/trx_title][vc_column_text]
<p style="font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.3em;">Youth Fire Stop is a program designed to prevent misuse of fire by youth in our community and to educate and intervene when endangerment involving fire occurs. Youth Fire Stop has been streamlined in order to make the program more effective.</p>

<p style="font-size: 1.37em; line-height: 1.36em;">Youth Fire Stop is a program designed to prevent misuse of fire by youth in our community and to educate and intervene when endangerment involving fire occurs. Youth Fire Stop has been streamlined in order to make the program more effective.</p>
[/vc_column_text][trx_button type="round" size="large" css="font-size: .92em;margin-top: 3.56em;"]view 2015 fire code[/trx_button][/trx_block][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content_no_spaces" css=".vc_custom_1450791886448{background-color: #f6f3f0 !important;}"][vc_column][trx_content][trx_title type="2" align="center" css="margin-top: 1.76em;" bottom="medium"]Public Assemblage[/trx_title][trx_blogger style="masonry_2" descr="230" cat="0" count="2" offset="0" css="margin-bottom: 3em;"][/trx_content][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content_no_spaces"][vc_column][trx_content][trx_title type="2" align="center" css="margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em;"]Industrial &amp; Commercial Fire Previntion[/trx_title][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1450794114657{margin-bottom: 3.4em !important;padding-right: 9% !important;padding-left: 9% !important;}"]
<p style="font-size: 1.37em; line-height: 1.36em; text-align: center;">The Industrial and Commercial Section has inspection responsibility of all High Rise buildings within the City on a annual basis.  Additionally, this section inspects complex and large industrial and commercial occupancies enforcing fire life safety regulations.</p>

[/vc_column_text][/trx_content][/trx_section][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][trx_content][trx_title type="2" align="center" animation="fadeIn" css="margin-top: 1.44em;" bottom="medium"]News &amp; Events[/trx_title][trx_blogger style="masonry_3" descr="130" cat="21" count="3" offset="0" animation="fadeIn"][/trx_content][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content_no_spaces"][vc_column][trx_section bg_image="954" bg_tile="" css="background-position:center;padding: 2.4em 0px;"][trx_content][trx_block class="max_width_responsive" css="max-width: 640px;"][trx_title type="3" animation="fadeIn" css="margin-bottom: .5em;"]Youth Fire Stop Prevention &amp; Intervention Program[/trx_title][vc_column_text]
<p style="font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.3em;">Youth Fire Stop is a program designed to prevent misuse of fire by youth in our community and to educate and intervene when endangerment involving fire occurs. Youth Fire Stop has been streamlined in order to make the program more effective.</p>

<p style="font-size: 1.4em; line-height: 1.3em;">Youth Fire Stop is a program designed to prevent misuse of fire by youth in our community and to educate and intervene when endangerment involving fire occurs. Youth Fire Stop has been streamlined in order to make the program more effective.</p>
